The DashboardComp component is designed for an admin dashboard to display key statistics and recent activity on the platform. 
It provides important insights into user and post counts, and shows tables with details about the most recent users and posts.

Key Features
User and Post Stats:

Displays the total number of users and total number of posts on the platform.
Shows the number of new users and posts from the previous month.
Recent Users and Posts:

Displays tables of the most recent users and posts with basic information:
User Table: Shows user profile images and usernames.
Post Table: Shows post images, titles, and categories.
